@couldbezah As a doctor working in the public health sector who has filled out too many death certificates to count, I can guarantee and assure you nobody is being paid to falsify documents or state covid-19 as a cause of death when it wasn’t. 
This pandemic is tough enough.

@couldbezah I know :) all I’m trying to say is that, on a death certificate, there is an “immediate” cause of death ie we would write covid-19 / pneumonia / whatever the patient acutely presented with, &then an “underlying” cause of death - which could be cancer, diabetes, hypertension etc.
